	<p><b>CARE FOR CREATION TIP</b>. The 50th anniversary of
Earth Day is coming in less than 60 days! Earth Day
Northwest 2020 is organizing local efforts to celebrate
this historic moment, focusing on three aspects: To
protect and preserve the natural environment, To
expect and commit to equity and inclusion, and To
ensure our built communities – cities and towns – are
safe, livable and healthy. To learn more, go to 
	<a target="_bulletin" href="https://earthdaynw2020.org/">https://earthdaynw2020.org/</a>.</p>


